TASK_REPORT_1_BODY=Go Binary Build Pipeline implemented. 5 files changed: (1) NEW shell/doey-go-helpers.sh — unified Go discovery, freshness check, build functions. (2) install.sh — uses shared helpers, builds both binaries explicitly. (3) doey.sh — source line added, build command exists, uninstall uses trash, doctor checks present. (4) pre-commit-go.sh — uses unified Go discovery. (5) on-pre-tool-use.sh — uses unified Go discovery. All pass bash -n and bash 3.2 compat (38 files, 0 violations). Success criteria: catalog done, install builds both, hooks use unified discovery, uninstall cleans up, doctor checks present.
